      <title>美国天然气价格暴跌势不可挡，损害了生产商</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/tumbling-us-natural-gas-prices-prove-unstoppable-hurting-producers-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近一年来，随着价格下跌，美国天然气生产商已踩刹车。但不断的产量增长，包括将天然气作为石油副产品开采的石油公司的产量增长，释放了创纪录的供应量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/tumbling-us-natural-gas-prices-prove-unstoppable-hurting-producers-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:14:04 GMT</pubDate>
